<h3 id="replace_copy_if">replace_copy_if</h3>

<p>For a range, copies the elements into another range, and replaces any element that passes a certain condition with a different value (that we specify) for the new range. DoesnŌĆÖt change the old range. (Ex. Replace all negative elements with a 0.)</p>

<ul>
